title: New lottery system
body:
Lower the cost of the ticket to 2 cakes and allow the subscription for more extractions.
Reshape the premium as follows:
4 numbers: 50%
3 numbers: 20%
2 numbers: 10%
1 lucky ticket (extracted from those played): 10%

Whoever wins the first prize and wants to collect everything immediately must burn 15% of the winnings, otherwise it will be paid daily in 1 month.
